message.entry: Field \"identifier\" of input structure must contain a valid MATLAB message identifier.
Field \"message\" of input structure must contain a character vector or string scalar.
The field \"stack\" must be an m-by-1 array.
The field \"stack\" must contain the fields: \"file\", \"name\", \"line\".
The field \"file\" of the field \"stack\" must contain a character vector.
The field \"line\" of the field \"stack\" must contain a scalar double.
The field \"name\" of the field \"stack\" must contain a character vector.
The field \"stack\" of the input structure must contain a structure.
